emerson radio  wikipedia emerson radio from wikipedia the free encyclopedia jump to navigation search not to be confused with emerson electric emerson radio corporation type public traded as nyse mkt msn industry wholesaler founded  headquarters hackensack new jersey usa key people duncan hon ceo products consumer electronics owner panasonic  funai present number of employees  website wwwemersonradiocom emerson radio corporation is one of the united states largest volume consumer electronics distributors and has a recognized trademark in continuous use since  the company designs markets and licenses many product lines worldwide including products sold and sometimes licensed under the brand name g clef a homage to emersons logo contents  history  –  –  –  –  –  –  –  –present  products  consumer electronics  hd radio  smartset  historical products  references  external links historyedit –edit emerson radio corp was incorporated in  as emerson phonograph co naics  consumer electronics wholesaling based in new york city by an early recording engineer and executive victor hugo emerson who was at one time employed by columbia records the first factories were opened in chicago and boston in  in december of that year the company fell victim to the sales slump for phonograph music that accompanied the postworld war i recession and the growth of commercial radio it went from the selfclaimed third largest record manufacturer into receivership –edit in  emerson phonograph co passed into the hands of benjamin abrams  and rudolph kanarak abrams a phonograph and record salesman along with his two brothers ran the company and renamed it emerson radio  phonograph corp in  after entering the radio business the companys record interests were subsequently sold although emerson introduced the first radiophonograph combination sold in the united states the company remained in obscurity until  when during the great depression it introduced the peewee radio see historical products below –